title: Snaps - Jimbo Fisher continues jabs at Nick Saban & Alabama, Oregon to the Big Ten, Is Texas Back?
itunes:title: Snaps - Jimbo Fisher continues jabs at Nick Saban & Alabama, Oregon to the Big Ten, Is Texas Back?
description:
Aaron Murray and T-Bob Hebert debut "SNAPS" by discussing Jimbo Fisher's continued criticism of Nick Saban and the Alabama Crimson Tide as well as Oregon's potential move to the Big Ten. Plus, Aaron gives his top 5 reasons Stetson will succeed in year 2 and T-Bob gives his top 5 candidates to sit on college football's Iron Throne. #Herd
